│ 330 /// it is 2 groups (%3 and %4)                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 331 /// %5 = shufflevector <8 x i16> %3, <8 x i16> poison,                                                                                                                                                     │
│ 332 ///    <4 x i32> <i32 0, i32 1, i32 2, i32 3>                                                                                                                                                              │
