│ 16289 /// Merges shuffle masks and emits final shuffle instruction, if required. It                                                                                                                            │
│ 16290 /// supports shuffling of 2 input vectors. It implements lazy shuffles emission,                                                                                                                         │
│ 16291 /// when the actual shuffle instruction is generated only if this is actually                                                                                                                            │
│ 16292 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed till the                                                                                                                            │
│ 16293 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions and further                                                                                                                         │
│ 16294 /// analysis/transformations.                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ 16295 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle instructions                                                                                                                         │
│ 16296 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                                                                                                                                                          │
│ 16297 /// For example, given the code                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ 16298 /// \code                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ 16299 /// %s1 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, poison, <1, 0>                                                                                                                                                      │
│ 16300 /// %s2 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %1, poison, <1, 0>                                                                                                                                                      │
│ 16301 /// \endcode                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 16302 /// and if need to emit shuffle of %s1 and %s2 with mask <1, 0, 3, 2>, it will                                                                                                                           │
│ 16303 /// look through %s1 and %s2 and emit                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ 16304 /// \code                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ 16305 /// %res = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, %1, <0, 1, 2, 3>                                                                                                                                                   │
│ 16306 /// \endcode                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 16307 /// instead.                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 16308 /// If 2 operands are of different size, the smallest one will be resized and                                                                                                                            │
│ 16309 /// the mask recalculated properly.                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ 16310 /// For example, given the code                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ 16311 /// \code                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ 16312 /// %s1 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, poison, <1, 0, 1, 0>                                                                                                                                                │
│ 16313 /// %s2 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %1, poison, <1, 0, 1, 0>                                                                                                                                                │
│ 16314 /// \endcode                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 16315 /// and if need to emit shuffle of %s1 and %s2 with mask <1, 0, 5, 4>, it will                                                                                                                           │
│ 16316 /// look through %s1 and %s2 and emit                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ 16317 /// \code                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ 16318 /// %res = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, %1, <0, 1, 2, 3>                                                                                                                                                   │
│ 16319 /// \endcode                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 16320 /// instead.                                                                                                                                                                                             │
